{"tid":2318743,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阻美核按鈕軍官進人民大會堂　中國特勤被打趴","createTime":"2020-12-09T14:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T05:35:18.000Z","uid":295230,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"7892172a439a31f413d11225da657b85d030de89","tid":2318743,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:35:31.000Z","msg":"美國新聞網站《Axios》周日（18日）報導，美國總統川普去年11月出訪中國時，因為中國人員不准手持「核彈發射手提箱」（Nuclear briefcase）的美國軍官，隨川普進入人民大會堂，美、中雙方的保安人員因此大打出手，連白宮幕僚長凱利（John Kelly）也參戰。<br />\n <br />\n《Axios》報導，川普當天出訪北京，預定到人民大會堂與中國國家主席習近平會面。沒想到，中國國家安全局的人員試圖阻止攜帶「核按鈕」手提箱的美國軍官入場。<br />\n <br />\n一名美國官員急忙向白宮幕僚長凱利報告。凱利得知後趕過去，並走到提箱軍官的身旁，讓他繼續前行。凱利也大聲向這名軍官及周圍的美國官員說：「我們進去」（we are moving in），隨即有中國維安人員抓住凱利的胳膊，凱利馬上甩開對方的手。<br />\n <br />\n之後美國特勤人員上前抓住動手的中國維安人員，並將他壓制在地。《Axios》稱，雙方肢體衝突發生在一瞬間，中國人員沒有碰到手提箱，後來中國的維安事務負責人向美國道歉，但要求美國人員不要對外張揚這起「美中大戰」。"},{"pid":"6abcf0836b5eb772343b80e423e3b30ddee5c0a2","tid":2318743,"uid":295230,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:35:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20180220/NXQEOL7GQXDFQJLZJRZ5XF2Q4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20180220%2FNXQEOL7GQXDFQJLZJRZ5XF2Q4Q%2F&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUM5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=e875fa2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20180220%2FNXQEOL7GQXDFQJLZJRZ5XF2Q4Q%2F&h=24d7db1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20180220/NXQEOL7GQXDFQJLZJRZ5XF2Q4Q/</a>"},{"pid":"90f0560a5237a5c00536aa7b9f67d575e27f662c","tid":2318743,"uid":31237,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:36:25.000Z","msg":"瘋了"},{"pid":"3f002d0cf2371b7ccde04b98285d7f6db44dd280","tid":2318743,"uid":39122,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>更新時間： 2018/02/20 01:40</blockquote>"},{"pid":"abeb4cc6b2ca1cc10958aa6bdf99027e0e14bf9f","tid":2318743,"uid":343294,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"在一旁的美國官員更是拍手叫好，不停大喊：『給我打，把他往死裡打！』"},{"pid":"eac91f5019e329f977130da4888c703c77adf608","tid":2318743,"uid":343294,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:43:38.000Z","msg":"當時川普、習近平這兩位大佬並沒有參與這次毆鬥，他們也沒有阻止好像一切與他兩無關。」"},{"pid":"871a54e0e0ca1013a9dc5a9bb20aede0ad08af28","tid":2318743,"uid":11097,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"abeb4cc6b2ca1cc10958aa6bdf99027e0e14bf9f","tid":2318743,"uid":343294,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"在一旁的美國官員更是拍手叫好，不停大喊：『給我打，把他往死裡打！』"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:44:34.000Z","msg":"屌我都諗起呢篇潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22671d2cdd777c5bfca8d0b2d06040184eda23a3","tid":2318743,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:45:49.000Z","msg":"以為往死裏打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ecc67c1cff15896c20c46c2463831670368407b","tid":2318743,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:46:07.000Z","msg":"我以為往死裏打"},{"pid":"4d8e15496d26ab91eafe8e227521957b1ad6e82b","tid":2318743,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"似流料喎"},{"pid":"159d56628d6171418880d3be4f54ef34ecfb571b","tid":2318743,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:47:47.000Z","msg":"嚴防竊密？美媒：美國防部長馬蒂斯返美前扔電腦手機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/733101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/733101</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb7090aa1f22ee349ad13026f1f6107facac8c8","tid":2318743,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T14:48:10.000Z","msg":"//雙方肢體衝突發生在一瞬間，中國人員沒有碰